://drarjunneurocare.com/about/#faq-2","name":"Do you accept insurance for neurology treatment?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, we work with all major insurance providers and TPA networks. Cashless facility is available. Our team assists with pre-authorisation and claim follow-up."}},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://drarjunneurocare.com/about/#faq-3","name":"How long does recovery take after a neurological procedure?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Recovery varies depending on the condition and procedure. Dr Arjun will provide a personalised aftercare plan with a realistic timeline at your consultation."}},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://drarjunneurocare.com/about/#faq-4","name":"Is EMI available for treatment packages?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, we offer zero-cost and low-cost EMI options through multiple bank partners. The approval process is quick and our team handles the paperwork."}},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://drarjunneurocare.com/about/#faq-5","name":"What are the clinic hours and location?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"We are open Monday to Saturday, 9:00 AM - 7:00 PM. Located at Plot 45, Kondapur Main Road, Kondapur, Hyderabad -- easily accessible from Gachibowli, Miyapur, and Madhapur."}}]}]}b:{"google":"https://g.page/drarjunneurocare","facebook":"https://facebook.com/drarjunneurocare","instagram":"https://instagram.com/drarjunneurocare","youtube":""}
